          of your system. It just works the way you'd expect.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-4">âŒ¨ï¸</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Media Controls</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Works with media keys, AirPods, and other Bluetooth headphones for
